metadata.name: Providence 12
metadata.description:
This collaborative FLOAT phase with drawing and AI, is an expression of the ups and downs of healing and being stuck in cycle until breakthrough comes.

The weightless moment between
Rising and falling,
The lift of a ride
Carrying me away
A safe moment passes-
Never to stay
I�m folded in-
The up and the down
As soon as the up is winning-
Here comes the down.
